253
00:22:40.551 --> 00:22:46.394
<i>"Buffalo soldiers." Hé, les gars.</i>

254
00:22:46.494 --> 00:22:49.398
<i>Et comment, je vous attends.</i>

255
00:22:49.498 --> 00:22:52.833
<i>Vous aurez tout ce que vous voulez.</i>

256
00:22:52.933 --> 00:22:56.804
